Public Sub HandleQuestAbandon(ByVal UserIndex As Integer)
'$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$
'Maneja el paquete QuestAbandon.
'Last modified: 31/01/2010 by Amraphen
'$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$
